类 SerializedStateHandle<T extends Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.state.AbstractCloseableHandle
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.state.memory.SerializedStateHandle<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - The type of state represented by this state handle.
    所有已实现的接口:
    Closeable, Serializable, AutoCloseable, StateHandle<T>, StateObject

    public class SerializedStateHandle<T extends Serializable>
extends AbstractCloseableHandle
implements StateHandle<T>
    A state handle that represents its state in serialized form as bytes.
